</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>Properties</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Activate further properties</strong> and check the box of the newly created property group.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.<br>
