<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-note" title="Note"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">First things first…​</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>This is a Best Practice for the online store plugin <strong>Ceres</strong>. <strong>Ceres</strong> is available in the <a href="https://marketplace.plentymarkets.com/plugins/templates/Ceres_4697" target="_blank" rel="noopener">plentyMarketplace</a> and runs on plentymarkets 7 systems.</p>
